<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="82r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l15">Coſtencʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l16"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt von den lewffen vnſers gnedıgſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l17"><expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıgs vnd auch des <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>cılıums</expan> / freẅntlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıben</expan> habt vvıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l18">dıe auf dıe ʒeit geſtalt warn Des wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l19">fleıſſ danken . Alſo <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l20">bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet ſouıl eẅch füklıch ſey wıe ſıch des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıgs vnd auch des <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>cılıu<ex>m</ex>s</expan> lewfft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l22">vnd ſache nu ſchıken vnd gemacht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch ob ır ıht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewfft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l23">oder mer weſt . dıe vns ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> gebüren . Vnd vns darinn eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l24"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſet als etc . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l25"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nerey et Achılley </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="82r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Costencz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst von den lewffen unsers
                        gnedigsten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> des
                            <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künigs, und auch des
                                <expan>co<ex>n</ex>ciliums</expan> frewntlich
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan> habt, wie die auf die zeit gestalt
                        warn, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        fleiss danken. Also <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey
                            <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, sovil ewch füklich sey, wie
                        sich des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        künigs, und auch des <expan>co<ex>n</ex>ciliu<ex>m</ex>s</expan> lewfft und
                        sache nu schiken und gemacht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch ob ir
                        iht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewfft oder mer west, die uns zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan> gebüren. Und uns darinn ewr
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und guten
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset, als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nerey et Achilley. </ab>
</div>
